As Wick faces betrayal and must confront the demons of his past, Ana De Armas’ character becomes a key ally, complicating the stakes in a world already on the brink of collapse.

This final installment promises heart-pounding action, breathtaking choreography, and emotional stakes as John Wick takes on a mission like no other. The shadows of his past catch up with him, forcing a confrontation that could define the future of the assassin world.

🎧Lyrics: 

[Verse 1]
I guess the time was right for us to say
We'd take our time and live our lives together day by day
We'll make a wish and send it on a prayer
We know our dreams can all come true with love that we can share

[Pre-Chorus]
With you I never wonder, will you be there for me?
With you I never wonder, you're the right one for me

[Chorus]
I finally found the love of a lifetime
A love to last my whole life through
I finally found the love of a lifetime
Forever in my heart, I finally found the love of a lifetime

[Verse 2]
With every kiss, our love is like brand new
And every star up in the sky was made for me and you
Still, we both know that the road is long
We know that we will be together because our love is strong

[Chorus]
I finally found the love of a lifetime
A love to last my whole life through
I finally found the love of a lifetime
Forever in my heart, I finally found the love of a lifetime

[Guitar Solo]

[Chorus]
Ooh, I finally found the love of a lifetime
A love to last my whole life through
I finally found the love of a lifetime
Forever in my heart, I finally found the love of a lifetime

[Outro]
(Finally found the love of a lifetime) Love of a lifetime
(Finally found the love of a lifetime) I finally found the love
(Finally found the love of a lifetime)
Ooh, forever in my heart, I finally found the love of a lifetime
Ooh-ooh, ooh
